Class ZIRegenAccessor

  • java.lang.Object

  • public abstract class ZIRegenAccessor
extends java.lang.Object
    THIS CLASS SHOULD NOT BE ACCESSED DIRECTLY BY EITHER THE CLIENT OR THE PLUGIN CODE.

    Provides the MEKON mechanisms with privileged access to the MEKON regenerated-instance representation.
